    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive wide-body 996.2 featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This specimen is mechanically flawless; the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with an LN Engineering ceramic solution, and the Rear Main Seal is bone dry. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, channeling power through a sophisticated viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. Handling is razor-sharp thanks to factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, while the four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers provide fade-free deceleration. This is a turn-key, investment-quality example for the enthusiast who demands peak longitudinal and lateral performance without compromise.",
      "price": 44900.0,
