    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, recently protected by a multi-stage professional ceramic coating. The alloy wheels are flawless, wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber with full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and taut with no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun-fading or rattles. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete and transparent service history housed in a dedicated binder. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no leaks or grime. This sale includes both original master keys, all factory manuals, and the original window sticker. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a like-new classic.",
